item.title: CVE-2021-24733|2024-08-03T19:42:16.560Z -- unknown -- wp%20post%20page%20clone
item.description: The WP Post Page Clone WordPress plugin before 1.2 allows users with a role as low as Contributor to clone and view other users' draft and password-protected posts which they cannot view normally.
